pot.com%2F-cReojy-u9rQ%2FUI2DQj7zJDI%2FAAAAAAAAE1Y%2F8IwpFo1CUX0%2Fs1600%2F28weekslaterposter.jpg&h=a5b6f7bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e2/The_Darkest_Hour_Theatrical_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe2%2FThe_Darkest_Hour_Theatrical_Poster.jpg&h=e8c68076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.Don和他的妻子Alice，還有另外一對年老的夫婦，還有其他兩個人，躲避在一個英國的農村房舍里。他們正在準備用餐，突然一個小男孩前來敲門，六個人起初不敢開門，因為怕染上狂暴病毒的殭屍襲擊他們，後來出於同情，還是將門給打開。但隨之而來的一群殭屍利用空隙闖了進來，並攻擊這些在屋內僅存的生還者。Alice與小孩被殭屍們追趕無路可逃，Don也無能為力，無法救出Alice與小孩，此刻的他也受到大批殭屍的追趕，自身難保的Don只得拚命的往前奔跑，最後乘坐一艘快艇逃跑，成為唯一的倖存者..<br />\n<br />\n2.講述一群年青的美國遊客在莫斯科旅遊時，遭遇外星物種入侵，奮力抵抗、掙扎求生的故事..<br />\n<br />\n12 10AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=87666172\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTDcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=315f1bcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80e08e5d5bace84ad123fcc72c8014070238342","tid":2170993,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf